<div id="q-how-share" class="question">
  <h3>10. How will you share the data?</h3>
  {%- scope -%}
  <div class="answer">
    {# Published datasets #}
    {%- set publishedDataPath = join([preservingCUuid, publishedDataQUuid], ".") -%}
    {%- set publishedDataCount = repliesMap[publishedDataPath].value.value -%}
    {%- if publishedDataCount && publishedDataCount > 0 -%}
      <ul>
      {%- for i in range(publishedDataCount-1) -%}
        {%- set pathPrefix = join([publishedDataPath, i], ".") -%}
        {%- set publishedDataName = repliesMap[join([pathPrefix, publishedDataNameQUuid], ".")].value.value -%}
        {%- set publishedDataLicensePath = join([pathPrefix, publishedDataLicenseQUuid], ".") -%}
        {%- set publishedDataLicenseAUuid = repliesMap[publishedDataLicensePath].value.value -%}
        {%- set publishedDataDOIPath = join([pathPrefix, publishedDataDOIQUuid], ".") -%}
        {%- set publishedDataDOIAUuid = repliesMap[publishedDataDOIPath].value.value -%}
        {%- if publishedDataLicenseAUuid || (publishedDataDOIAUuid == publishedDataDOIYesAUuid) -%}
          <li>
            <strong>{{ publishedDataName ? publishedDataName : "(no name given)" }}</strong>
            {%- if publishedDataLicenseAUuid == publishedDataLicenseCC0AUuid %}
              <span class="separator">&ndash;</span> freely available for any use (public domain or CC0).
            {%- elif publishedDataLicenseAUuid == publishedDataLicenseCCBYAUuid %}
              <span class="separator">&ndash;</span> freely available with obligation to quote the source (e.g. CC-BY).
            {%- elif publishedDataLicenseAUuid == publishedDataLicenseRestrictAUuid -%}
              {%- set licenseRestrictConditionsPath = join([publishedDataLicensePath, publishedDataLicenseRestrictAUuid, licenseRestrictConditionsQUuid], ".") -%}
              {%- set licenseRestrictConditions = repliesMap[licenseRestrictConditionsPath].value.value -%}
              {%- set licenseRestrictAccessPath = join([publishedDataLicensePath, publishedDataLicenseRestrictAUuid, licenseRestrictAccessQUuid], ".") -%}
              {%- set licenseRestrictAccessAUuid = repliesMap[licenseRestrictAccessPath].value.value -%}
              {%- set licenseRestrictMetadataPath = join([publishedDataLicensePath, publishedDataLicenseRestrictAUuid, licenseRestrictMetadataQUuid], ".") -%}
              {%- set licenseRestrictMetadataAUuid = repliesMap[licenseRestrictMetadataPath].value.value %}
              <span class="separator">&ndash;</span> available under some restrictions, which we will follow in our project{{ licenseRestrictConditions ? ": " ~ licenseRestrictConditions : "" }}{{ endswith(licenseRestrictConditions, ".") ? "" : "." }}
              {%- if licenseRestrictAccessAUuid == licenseRestrictAccessRequestAUuid %}
                Re-users will be able to get access by request to the contact person.
              {%- elif licenseRestrictAccessAUuid == licenseRestrictAccessCommitteeAUuid %}
                Re-users will be able to get access through a <em>Data Access Committee</em> for the project.
              {%- elif licenseRestrictAccessAUuid == licenseRestrictAccessAnotherAUuid -%}
                {%- set licenseRestrictAccessAnotherPath = join([licenseRestrictAccessPath, licenseRestrictAccessAnotherAUuid, licenseRestrictAccessAnotherQUuid], ".") -%}
                {%- set licenseRestrictAccessAnother = repliesMap[licenseRestrictAccessAnotherPath].value.value %}
                Re-users will be able to get access through a specialized process{{ licenseRestrictAccessAnother ? ": " ~ licenseRestrictAccessAnother : "" }}{{ endswith(licenseRestrictAccessAnother, ".") ? "" : "." }}
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- if licenseRestrictMetadataAUuid == licenseRestrictMetadataYesAUuid %}
                The conditions will be published as part of open metadata.
              {%- endif -%}
              {%- if publishedDataDOIAUuid == publishedDataDOIYesAUuid -%}
                {%- set publishedDataDOIYesWhatPath = join([publishedDataDOIPath, publishedDataDOIYesAUuid, publishedDataDOIYesWhatQUuid], ".") -%}
                {%- set publishedDataDOIYesWhat = repliesMap[publishedDataDOIYesWhatPath].value.value -%}
                {%- if publishedDataDOIYesWhat %}
                  The DOI for this data set is <a href="https://doi.org/{{ publishedDataDOIYesWhat }}" target="_blank">{{ publishedDataDOIYesWhat }}</a>.
                {%- else %}
                  We will get a DOI for this data set.
                {%- endif -%}
              {%- endif -%}
            {%- endif -%}
          </li>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
      </ul>
    {%- endif -%}
    
    <p>Information about used repositories (i.e. where will potential users find out about the data) is provided in Section E, Question 9.</p>

    <p>Embargo on the data is described in Section C, Question 5, and Section F, Question 11.</p>
  </div>
  {%- endscope -%}
</div>
